It concerns two missions to Minas Gerais and Brasilia (a workshop) in October and November of 2019, to work with ANM (National Mining Agency of Brazil) and various stakeholders, in particular to share knowledge from the Dutch experience with dykes and levees. In particular it concerns preventing insecurity that results from too weak mining dams and dykes.
